        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/h/b4bc9f/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2021-08-28T07:25:20.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I got this 2019 Vosne Romanee bottle from a Belgian importer . I had never heard about this domaine , he said it was very good and I should give it a try . Well , I\u2019m glad I did as this was a stunning bottle of delicious pinot . We finished the bottle in no time , it was already perfectly ready .<br>\nWith all these crazy prices , I am always looking out for a newcomer where the prices are more normal . This could be one ( no mention on Burghound , Vinous or Wine Advocate ) .<br>\nI think he also makes a few premier cru\u2019s and even Echezeaux , I will definitely try to find more .</p>",
        "post_number": 1,
        "post_type": 1,
        "posts_count": 11,
        "updated_at": "2022-06-04T07:34:47.067Z",
